something romantic.

13:34.446 --> 13:36.079
Like oysters?
No, I'm making haggis.

13:36.080 --> 13:38.883
It's a sheep's stomach
served dumpling-style.

13:40.452 --> 13:42.252
Mmm.

13:47.392 --> 13:49.927
Hey!
Hi, sweetie.

13:49.928 --> 13:51.462
Great news.

13:51.463 --> 13:55.265
Wilson is making judith's
breasts out of clay.

13:55.266 --> 13:56.600
What?

13:56.601 --> 13:59.603
