He's crazy about her.

13:59.604 --> 14:01.338
Oh, no.

14:01.339 --> 14:06.209
What do you mean, "oh, no"?
This is what you wanted.

14:06.210 --> 14:07.878
I've just been
talking to judith.

14:07.879 --> 14:09.980
She's having serious doubts
about the relationship.

14:09.981 --> 14:12.382
Oh, no.

14:12.383 --> 14:17.455
