has a problem with intimacy.

14:17.456 --> 14:18.589
Oh!

14:18.590 --> 14:22.693
So he can't...
Oh. Oh, god. Oh!

14:22.694 --> 14:23.828
Oh!

14:23.829 --> 14:25.996
Well... Oh, honey!

14:25.997 --> 14:28.098
I mean, I would have
never known.

14:28.099 --> 14:30.434
