something like that.

14:30.435 --> 14:32.603
No wonder he's got
all this...

14:32.604 --> 14:34.371
Probably an old war injury
or something, huh?

14:34.372 --> 14:39.076
Not that kind of intimacy!
I'm talking about
emotional intimacy.

14:39.077 --> 14:42.780
Thank god it's nothing
important. Whoo!

14:44.950 --> 14:46.450
He doesn't share
his feelings.

14:46.451 --> 14:48.619
She's spent every day
the last two weeks with him,

14:48.620 --> 14:50.387
