who he is.

14:50.388 --> 14:53.958
I've spent the last
15 years with him,
and I don't know who he is.

14:53.959 --> 14:55.626
It doesn't hurt
our relationship.

14:55.627 --> 14:58.462
I think she wants something
more from the relationship.

14:58.463 --> 15:00.397
She wants to go
to the next level.

15:00.398 --> 15:04.067
What is it with you women
and the "next level"?

15:04.068 --> 15:06.103
What's wrong with
the level we're on?

15:06.104 --> 15:10.140
Just take the elevator
and leave us
the heck alone. Hmm?

15:10.141 --> 15:11.976
Every time she asks him
about himself,

15:11.977 --> 15:13.811
